     F** ABMR21 *********************************************
     F*設定数自動処理　メッキかんばんマスタ更新           *
     F* AUTO CHANGE MONTHLY SETTING # - UPDATE AAFPP01      *
     F*    HOTTA.            2018.06.11                     *
     F*----------+-----+----------+-----------------------------------*
     F*2021.03.09|DCS. |T.MITSUI  | CHANGE WITH THE NUMBER OF FIGURES *
     F*          |     |          |          EXPANSION OF THE "KANBAN"*
     F* CANCEL SPECIAL ADJUSTMENT                           *
     F*    C.SAKTHIP         2025.03.01                     *
     F*****************************************************************
     FABMWP21 UF  E                    DISK
     FGHCTL21 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAFTL06 UF  E           K        DISK
     FABMWP30 O   E           K        DISK                      A
     FABMWP31 O   E                    DISK                      A
     FABMPPB5 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABMPPB6 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABMPL21 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  100A3UKBI
     I                                        1   40A3UKYY
     I                                        5   60A3UKMM
     I                                        7   80A3UKDD
     I                                        9  100A3UBIN
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  100A3TKBI
     I                                        1   40A3TKYY
     I                                        5   60A3TKMM
     I                                        7   80A3TKDD
     I                                        9  100A3TBIN
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A3KOHZ
     I                                        5   80A3KOMD
