     I                                        6   7 ATKR3
     I                                        9   9 ATKR4
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     I              '0123456789'          C         WKCKSU
     I              'OVER 1000'           C         ERR01
